  "name": "RPlog_The_Wargames_Begin",
  "title": "Mock Battle Over Ord Mantell",
  "summary": "The New Republic's Second Fleet stages a massive wargame over Ord Mantell, with the defending forces awaiting an 'Opposite Force' standing in for the Imperials, complete with Star Destroyers and aggressive A-wing 'Falcon' squadrons. Aboard the refitted corvette Audacity, executive officer Rasi -- callsign Krayt Control -- coordinates his battered ship and its fighter screen against an enemy Loromar Strike Cruiser. The dogfight is carried by Ghost Squadron, including the Sullustan Jedi reservist Ikihsa Enb'Zik in Ghost 10 and the brash Lance 'Wildman' Corbet in Ghost Six, who duel against the Black Hammer A-wing pilots Raxis 'Spider' L'ygr, the Mon Calamari 'Fishbreath' in Hammer Six, and the peaceable Ithorian Nail in Hammer Seven. Enb'Zik uses the Force to outfly his scrambler-equipped foes, while Wildman wins a game of chicken to power down Hammer Six. Rasi then directs Wildman to slip behind the Strike Cruiser and torpedo its engines and weapons, crippling the larger ship as the Audacity presses its advantage and the simulated battle turns in the Republic's favor.",
